<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-233] 30.4.3. Running the Test Suite</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-233</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Please include how to run this on a Lustre system that has multiple machines and a real physical Lustre targets.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are changes needed to the test configuration to identify resources for test to use.  This is mostly about how to configure the test suites. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;./llmount.sh only proves that your configuration works and only works by default on a Lustre system that is ran on a single machine. It is not really a test for Lustre. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
